//gaTogglePartyToken.cs - Switches the player token to the party token or the normal selected party leader token (or group)
//parm1 = (string) the filename (no extension) of the party token or leave blank ("") or "none" if you wish to use the existing party token
//parm2 = (bool) false = turn off party token, true = turn on party token; when setting this to false, additional and absolute party speed are set to 0 automatically
//parm3 = (int) absolute party speed with this vehicle, not affected by traits or attributes, use 0 or higher; using "none" will leave speed unchanged  
//parm4 = (int) additional party speed with this vehicle,  additoinally affected by traits or attributes, use 0 or higher; using "none" will leave speed unchanged 
